    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged and judged acceptable given that the ASTM F1717 protocol specifies a single standardized test configuration and that all three QoIs satisfy acceptance bounds with E/uval ratios well below 1.96. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision. Note: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; the digital signature workflow is pending organizational PKI provisioning and will be applied prior to final archival submission.",
